processVariable.name: instanceDetails

TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlString select LBSC.STATUS_ID as statusID, LBSC."NAME" as status, LP."NAME" as ApplicationName, count(*) as instanceCount from LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES LBSC, LSW_BPD_INSTANCE LBI, LSW_PROJECT LP where LBI.EXECUTION_STATUS = LBSC.STATUS_ID and LBI.PROJECT_ID = LP.PROJECT_ID and LBI.LAST_MODIFIED_DATETIME <= (SYSDATE - ?) and LBSC.STATUS_ID IN <#=tw.local.statusIN#> and LP.SHORT_NAME IN <#=tw.local.appIN#> group by LBSC.name, LP."NAME", LBSC.STATUS_ID
